<p>most marvellous escape for so very few of these big shells are duds, they not only shot every size shell they had at us but we also had to face the gas &amp; tear shell which they plastered on to us, &amp; on top of that again the liquid fire shell was showered on us Hell was no name for it, but even this tornado of fire failed to move our chaps About 7 oclock they evidently thought every man was killed &amp; they were not very far out, but still when the Prussian Guards changed they got the shock of their lives for they got cut to ribbons &amp; the few remaining</p>
